    "result": {"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Ramadan Learning Phase: Real Electrical Field Work Begins","description":"Skipping idle time during Diploma result wait — jumping into real electrical wiring, house wiring, and maintenance practice at my uncle shop.","slug":"/pensieve/ramadan-electrical-field-practice","date":"2026-03-05T00:00:00.000Z","tags":["Electrical","Diploma","Fieldwork","Wiring","Learning"],"draft":false},"html":"<p>Ramadan this year is not just about ibadah — it has become a serious <strong>learning phase</strong> for me.</p>\n<p>My Diploma in Electrical Engineering result is still not published. Instead of wasting this waiting period, I made a decision: use this time wisely by doing real field practice at my uncle's electrical shop.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/09966004e2486873a71d327eb993b9f5/008f5/tota.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.85714285714286%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Practice at uncle&#39;s shop\"\n        title=\"Practice at uncle&#39;s shop\"\n        src=\"/static/09966004e2486873a71d327eb993b9f5/03346/tota.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/09966004e2486873a71d327eb993b9f5/71299/tota.jpg 175w,\n/static/09966004e2486873a71d327eb993b9f5/1e9fe/tota.jpg 350w,\n/static/09966004e2486873a71d327eb993b9f5/03346/tota.jpg 700w,\n/static/09966004e2486873a71d327eb993b9f5/c3223/tota.jpg 1050w,\n/static/09966004e2486873a71d327eb993b9f5/da6ee/tota.jpg 1400w,\n/static/09966004e2486873a71d327eb993b9f5/008f5/tota.jpg 4000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>What I'm Practicing</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Wiring</li>\n<li>House wiring</li>\n<li>Electrical maintenance</li>\n<li>Basic electronics device repair</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Classroom vs Field</h2>\n<p>In Bangladesh, polytechnic and training centers often fall short on the practical side. Theory is taught well, but hands-on skills? That's a different story.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Working directly in the field is a completely different experience. Every connection, every fault, every fix teaches something new.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7703ecb352c5b9a1e682552b24f8fa05/008f5/tota-1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.85714285714286%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Learning in action\"\n        title=\"Learning in action\"\n        src=\"/static/7703ecb352c5b9a1e682552b24f8fa05/03346/tota-1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7703ecb352c5b9a1e682552b24f8fa05/71299/tota-1.jpg 175w,\n/static/7703ecb352c5b9a1e682552b24f8fa05/1e9fe/tota-1.jpg 350w,\n/static/7703ecb352c5b9a1e682552b24f8fa05/03346/tota-1.jpg 700w,\n/static/7703ecb352c5b9a1e682552b24f8fa05/c3223/tota-1.jpg 1050w,\n/static/7703ecb352c5b9a1e682552b24f8fa05/da6ee/tota-1.jpg 1400w,\n/static/7703ecb352c5b9a1e682552b24f8fa05/008f5/tota-1.jpg 4000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>What's Next</h2>\n<p>After this one month, <strong>In Sha Allah</strong>, I plan to move to <strong>Gazipur</strong> for more advanced learning and to begin my job search.</p>\n<p>This journey to become a skilled electrical professional has officially started — one wire at a time.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"My Poem \"Ami Shadhinota Bolchi\" Published in Daily Amar Bangla (July 2023)","description":"My Bengali poem “Ami Shadhinota Bolchi” was published in Daily Amar Bangla in July 2023. A proud achievement highlighting freedom, protest, and social awareness.","slug":"/pensieve/poem-ami-shadhinota-bolchi","date":"2023-07-01T00:00:00.000Z","tags":["Writing","Poetry","Achievement","Bangladesh","Creative"],"draft":false},"html":"<h2>📰 আমার কবিতা পত্রিকায় প্রকাশিত — “আমি স্বাধীনতা বলছি”</h2>\n<p>একটা বিশেষ মুহূর্ত শেয়ার করতে চাই…</p>\n<p>আমার লেখা কবিতা <strong>“আমি স্বাধীনতা বলছি”</strong> প্রকাশিত হয়েছিল <strong>জুলাই ২০২৩</strong>-এ, <strong>দৈনিক আমার বাংলা</strong> পত্রিকায়। এটা আমার জন্য অনেক বড় একটা অর্জন এবং গর্বের বিষয়।</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/60c79cb8e562ab8b0cc6e8665893850c/87945/paper.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 155.99999999999997%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Published newspaper\"\n        title=\"Published newspaper\"\n        src=\"/static/60c79cb8e562ab8b0cc6e8665893850c/03346/paper.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/60c79cb8e562ab8b0cc6e8665893850c/71299/paper.jpg 175w,\n/static/60c79cb8e562ab8b0cc6e8665893850c/1e9fe/paper.jpg 350w,\n/static/60c79cb8e562ab8b0cc6e8665893850c/03346/paper.jpg 700w,\n/static/60c79cb8e562ab8b0cc6e8665893850c/87945/paper.jpg 1024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>📖 কবিতার ভাবনা</h2>\n<p>এই কবিতায় আমি স্বাধীনতার কথা বলেছি—<br>\nকিন্তু শুধু ইতিহাসের স্বাধীনতা না,<br>\nবরং বর্তমান সমাজের অন্যায়, নীরবতা এবং প্রতিবাদের কথাও তুলে ধরার চেষ্টা করেছি।</p>\n<h2>✍️ আমার অনুভূতি</h2>\n<p>ছোটবেলা থেকে লেখালেখির প্রতি আগ্রহ ছিল,<br>\nকিন্তু নিজের লেখা print আকারে দেখতে পাওয়া — সত্যিই অন্যরকম অনুভূতি।</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/772edc8c7aa38a39fec760e941ae5ec4/3c48b/paper1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 198.85714285714283%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Newspaper clipping\"\n        title=\"Newspaper clipping\"\n        src=\"/static/772edc8c7aa38a39fec760e941ae5ec4/03346/paper1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/772edc8c7aa38a39fec760e941ae5ec4/71299/paper1.jpg 175w,\n/static/772edc8c7aa38a39fec760e941ae5ec4/1e9fe/paper1.jpg 350w,\n/static/772edc8c7aa38a39fec760e941ae5ec4/03346/paper1.jpg 700w,\n/static/772edc8c7aa38a39fec760e941ae5ec4/3c48b/paper1.jpg 965w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>🚀 What's Next</h2>\n<p>এই যাত্রা এখানেই শেষ না—<br>\nলেখালেখি এবং নিজের skill development—দুইটাই একসাথে এগিয়ে নিতে চাই, In Sha Allah।</p>\n<p>সবাই দোয়া রাখবেন 🤍</p>"}}]}},"pageContext":{}},
